        "content": "#!/bin/bash\r\nPID_FILE=/home/engines/run/openfire.pid\r\n\r\nif ! test -f /home/engines/run/flags/dbssetup\r\n then\r\n  cat resources/database/openfire_mysql.sql  |mysql -h mysql -u $dbuser --password=$dbpasswd $dbname\r\n  touch /home/engines/run/flags/dbssetup\r\nfi\r\ncd /home/app\r\n. /home/engines/functions/trap.sh\r\nulimit\r\nbin/openfire start\r\necho $! >$PID_FILE\r\nstartup_complete\r\n\r\nwhile ! test -f /home/engines/run/flags/sig_term \r\n do \r\n  sleep 10 &\r\n  ps -ax |grep java |grep -v grep \r\n  if test $? -ne 0\r\n   then\r\n    break\r\n  fi    \r\n  wait \r\ndone  \r\n\r\nrm $PID_FILE\r\nshutdown_complete"
